---
title: White Zucchini and Ricotta Pizza with Garden Salad
description: Pay homage to the end of the summer season with a delicious white zucchini pizza. A sneaky favourite amongst pizza fans, this pizza uses ricotta as a base, then is topped with lemon-seasoned zucchini, and mozzarella. To sweeten the deal, we've thrown in a fresh veg-packed garden salad that can either be eaten on the side or topped on a slice to unlock a new flavour combo you didn't know you needed!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pizza-blanche-aux-courgettes-et-a-la-ricotta-7470dc39.jpg
